blog.name: impainting-impaintingagain
blog.title: McLain Art & Design
blog.description:
Abigail is a visual artist based in Kalamazoo, Michigan. Her work is primarily inspired by psychology, horror, tattoo design, and anatomy. Though she is most well known for her ink and watercolor illustrations, she enjoys working in a variety of mediums. Through her conceptual work, she hopes to bring awareness to issues surrounding trauma and mental illness.
